Part1
If anyone wants to purchase a house the price of the houses differ variously in the same local hood.For that reason I want to produce a model which can easily produce the prices of the houses as per requirement. And for that I need foursquare location data to produce a define the price of houses as per area requirements as well as all the supplies or services near any house. 
It is necessary for the people or audience which want to purchase a certain house. Because as they are purchasing a house they want a perfect neighborhood in which they can live happily ever after. 

